, "pid": 292034, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "其实这题还有一个很关键的事情：如果选A的人数多，大家的分数都会比较高，那么老师会调分，这样其实是选A扣3分左右，选B加5分左右", "timestamp": 1618896453, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1485592, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Hans", "pid": 292034, "reply_to": 1485582, "tag": null, "text": "Re Hans: 而且如果赌输了，代表加分人不超过一半", "timestamp": 1618896488, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1485594, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Isabella", "pid": 292034, "reply_to": 1485584, "tag": null, "text": "这样算的话其实是果断选B（不过Isabella之前没想到这一层选了A）", "timestamp": 1618896496, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1485634, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Jason", "pid": 292034, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "似乎15个A15个B是个纳什均衡?", "timestamp": 1618896943, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1485728, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 292034, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "若A多，a比b多两分，按等级制大概只有不到一半升级，基本没有\n若B多，b比a多10分，80b～b-直接起飞90a-\n综上如果老师只搞一次果断b，但是次数多了就不好说了我也不知道会怎么样", "timestamp": 1618898075, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1485924, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Louis", "pid": 292034, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我直接联系教务处", "timestamp": 1618900785, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1485968, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Margaret", "pid": 292034, "reply_to": 1485924, "tag": null, "text": "Re Louis: 笑死 不要这么现实啊", "timestamp": 1618901434, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1485986, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Nathan", "pid": 292034, "reply_to": -1, "tag": null, "text": "我感觉不考虑最终的等级啥的，就从这一次选择给自己带来（相比给别人）带来更多的得分，那么B应该是优势策略吧......", "timestamp": 1618901603, "type": "text", "url": ""}, {"cid": 1485991, "deleted": false, "image_metadata": {}, "is_dz": false, "name": "Kate", "pid": 292034, "reply_to": 1485924, "tag": null, "text": "Re Loui